dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Seboyeta Quadrangle, New Mexico
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Geology of the Seboyeta Quadrangle, New Mexico. Alternate title series: Geologic Quadrangle map of the United States. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Datum is mean sea level. "Geology mapped in 1956."
